e%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOver%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20I%20will%20be%20attending%20various%20programmes%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20development%20works%20which%20will%20be%20inaugurated%20cover%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20sectors%20and%20will%20transform%20several%20lives.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdNp6tLs26e%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdNp6tLs26e%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1764322516766724483%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%204%2C%20at%20around%2010%3A30%20am%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20inaugurate%2C%20dedicate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%2056%2C000%20crore%20in%20Adilabad%2C%20Telangana%2C%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20at%20around%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20visit%20BHAVINI%20in%20Kalpakkam%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%205%2C%20at%20around%2011%20am%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%2C%20dedicate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20Rs%206%2C800%20crore%20in%20Sangareddy%2C%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20he%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20over%20Rs%2019%2C600%20crore%20at%20Chandikhole%2C%20Jajpur%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20at%20around%2010%3A15%20am%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20connectivity%20projects%20worth%20Rs%2015%2C400%20crore%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20visit%20Bettiah%20in%20Bihar%20at%20around%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20where%20he%20will%20inaugurate%2C%20dedicate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20around%20Rs%2012%2C800%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20public%20programme%20in%20Adilabad%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20projects%20related%20to%20power%2C%20rail%20and%20road%20sector%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%2056%2C000%20crore.%20The%20major%20focus%20of%20the%20projects%20will%20be%20the%20power%20sector%2C%20the%20PMO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%2C%20dedicate%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20various%20projects%20related%20to%20the%20power%20sector%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20dedicate%20NTPC's%20800%20MW%20(Unit-2)%20of%20Telangana%20Super%20Thermal%20Power%20Project%20in%20Peddapalli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Ultra-Supercritical%20Technology%2C%20the%20project%20will%20supply%2085%20per%20cent%20power%20to%20Telangana%20and%20will%20have%20the%20highest%20power%20generation%20efficiency%20of%20approximately%2042%20per%20cent%20among%20all%20power%20stations%20of%20NTPC%20in%20India.%20The%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20project%20was%20also%20laid%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20also%20dedicate%20660%20MW%20(Unit-2)%20of%20North%20Karanpura%20Super%20Thermal%20Power%20Project%20in%20Chatra%2C%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20country's%20first%20Supercritical%20Thermal%20Power%20Project%20conceived%20with%20an%20air-cooled%20condenser%20of%20such%20large%20magnitude%20which%20reduces%20water%20consumption%20to%20one-third%20in%20comparison%20to%20conventional%20water-cooled%20condensers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commencement%20of%20work%20in%20this%20project%20was%20flagged%20off%20by%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20will%20also%20dedicate%20the%20Fly%20Ash%20Based%20Light%20Weight%20Aggregate%20Plant%20at%20Sipat%2C%20Bilaspur%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20STP%20Water%20to%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Plant%20at%20Greater%20Noida%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20will%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20Singrauli%20Super%20Thermal%20Power%20Project%2C%20Stage-III%20(2x800%20MW)%20in%20Sonbhadra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3B%20Flue%20Gas%20CO2%20to%204G%20Ethanol%20Plant%20at%20Lara%2C%20Raigarh%20in%20Chhattisgarh%3B%20Sea%20Water%20to%20Green%20Hydrogen%20plant%20at%20Simhadri%2C%20Visakhapatnam%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3B%20and%20Fly%20Ash%20Based%20FALG%20Aggregate%20Plant%20at%20Korba%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20seven%20projects%20and%20also%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20one%20project%20of%20Power%20Grid%20Corporation%20of%20India.%20These%20projects%20will%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20strengthening%20the%20National%20Grid%2C%20the%20PMO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20will%20also%20inaugurate%20National%20Hydroelectric%20Power%20Corporation's%20(NHPC's)%20380%20MW%20solar%20project%20at%20Jaisalmer%2C%20Rajasthan.%20Around%20792%20million%20units%20of%20green%20power%20will%20be%20generated%20each%20year%20from%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20Bundelkhand%20Saur%20Urja%20Limited's%201%2C200%20MW%20Jalaun%20Ultra%20Mega%20Renewable%20Energy%20Power%20Park%20in%20Jalaun%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20park%20will%20generate%20about%202%2C400%20million%20units%20of%20electricity%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20will%20inaugurate%20three%20solar%20power%20projects%20of%20Satluj%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20(SJVN)%20in%20Jalaun%20and%20Kanpur%20Dehat%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20These%20projects%20have%20a%20total%20capacity%20of%20200%20MW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFoundation%20stone%20of%20these%20projects%20was%20also%20laid%20by%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20inaugurate%20Naitwar%20Mori%20hydro%20power%20station%20along%20with%20associated%20transmission%20line%20in%20Uttarkashi%2C%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20projects%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20also%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20two%20solar%20projects%20of%20SJVN%20in%20Bilaspur%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%26amp%3B%20Dhubri%2C%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20power%20sector%2C%20projects%20of%20the%20road%20and%20rail%20sector%20will%20also%20be%20taken%20up%20during%20the%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20will%20dedicate%20the%20newly%20electrified%20Ambari-Adilabad-Pimpalkhuti%20rail%20line%20to%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20also%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20two%20major%20national%20highway%20projects%20connecting%20Telangana%20with%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Telangana%20with%20Chhattisgarh%20through%20NH-353B%20and%20NH-163.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sangareddy%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20development%20projects%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%206%2C800%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20projects%20encompass%20multiple%20key%20sectors%20like%20road%2C%20rail%2C%20petroleum%20and%20natural%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20three%20national%20highway%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20programme%2C%20he%20will%20also%20inaugurate%20doubling%20and%20electrification%20of%20Sanathnagar%20-%20Moula%20Ali%20rail%20line%20along%20with%20six%20new%20station%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%2022-km%20route%20of%20the%20project%20has%20been%20commissioned%20with%20automatic%20signalling%20and%20has%20been%20completed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20MMTS%20(Multi%20Modal%20Transport%20Service)%20Phase-II%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20it%2C%20six%20new%20station%20buildings%20have%20come%20up%20at%20Ferozguda%2C%20Suchitra%20Centre%2C%20Bhudevi%20Nagar%2C%20Ammuguda%2C%20Neredmet%20and%20Moula%20Ali%20Housing%20Board%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20will%20also%20flag%20off%20the%20inaugural%20MMTS%20Train%20Service%20from%20Ghatkesar-Lingampalli%20via%20Moula%20Ali-Sanathnagar.%20This%20train%20service%20extends%20the%20popular%20suburban%20train%20service%20in%20the%20Hyderabad-Secunderabad%20twin%20city%20regions%20to%20new%20areas%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20inaugurate%20the%20Indian%20Oil%20Paradip-Hyderabad%20Product%20Pipeline.%20He%20will%20also%20inaugurate%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Research%20Organization%20(CARO)%20centre%20in%20Hyderabad.%20It%20has%20been%20set%20up%20at%20Begumpet%20Airport%2C%20Hyderabad%20by%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20to%20upgrade%20and%20enhance%20the%20research%20and%20development%20activities%20in%20the%20civil%20aviation%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kalpakkam%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20marking%20a%20historic%20milestone%20in%20India's%20nuclear%20power%20programme%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20witness%20the%20initiation%20of%20core%20loading%20of%20India's%20indigenous%20Prototype%20Fast%20Breeder%20Reactor%20(PFBR)%20of%20500%20MWe%20capacity.%20This%20PFBR%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20BHAVINI%20(Bharatiya%20Nabhikiya%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20Limited).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reactor%20core%20consists%20of%20control%20subassemblies%2C%20blanket%20subassemblies%20and%20fuel%20subassemblies.%20The%20core%20loading%20activity%20consists%20of%20loading%20of%20reactor%20control%20subassemblies%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20blanket%20subassemblies%20and%20the%20fuel%20sub-assemblies%20which%20will%20generate%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chandikhole%2C%20Odisha%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20inaugurate%2C%20dedicate%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20over%20Rs%2019%2C600%20crore.%20The%20projects%20relate%20to%20sectors%20including%20oil%20%26amp%3B%20gas%2C%20railways%2C%20road%2C%20and%20atomic%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kolkata%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20enhancing%20avenues%20for%20ensuring%20ease%20of%20urban%20mobility%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20Kolkata%20Metro's%20Howrah%20Maidan-Esplanade%20Metro%20section%2C%20Kavi%20Subhash-Hemanta%20Mukhopadhyay%20Metro%20section%2C%20Taratala-Majerhat%20Metro%20section%20(part%20of%20Joka-Esplanade%20line)%3B%20Pune%20Metro%20from%20Ruby%20Hall%20Clinic%20to%20Ramwadi%20stretch%3B%20Kochi%20Metro%20Rail%20Phase%20I%20Extension%20project%20(Phase%20IB)%20from%20SN%20Junction%20Metro%20station%20to%20Tripunithura%20Metro%20station%3B%20Agra%20Metro's%20stretch%20from%20Taj%20East%20Gate%20to%20Mankameshwar%3B%20and%20Duhai-Modinagar%20(North)%20section%20of%20Delhi-Meerut%20RRTS%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20flag%20off%20train%20services%20on%20these%20sections.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20also%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20extension%20of%20Pune%20Metro%20Rail%20project%20phase%201%20between%20Pimpri%20Chinchwad%20Metro-Nigdi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709520660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fdfa3erjg_pm-modi-rally_625x300_04_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-begin-5-state-tour-today-to-launch-projects-worth-rs-1-10-600-crore-5171577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20visit%20Telangana%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Odisha%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Bihar%20on%20March%204-6%2