nd%20nothing%20is%20known%20(about)%20what%20happened%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chander%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai-headquartered%20Western%20Naval%20Command%20stated%20that%20a%20high-level%20board%20of%20inquiry%20has%20been%20initiated%20to%20find%20Mr%20Verma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%2C%20Sahil%20Verma%2C%20Seaman%20II%2C%20has%20been%20reported%20missing%20at%20sea%20from%20(an)%20Indian%20Naval%20Ship%20whilst%20on%20deployment%20since%20February%2027%2C%202024.%20The%20Navy%20immediately%20launched%20a%20massive%20search%20operation%20with%20ships%20and%20aircraft%2C%20which%20is%20still%20continuing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%2C%20Sahil%20Verma%2C%20Seaman%20II%2C%20has%20been%20reported%20missing%20at%20sea%20from%20Indian%20Naval%20Ship%20whilst%20on%20deployment%20since%2027%20Feb%2024.%20The%20Navy%20immediately%20launched%20a%20massive%20search%20operation%20with%20ships%20and%20aircraft%2C%20which%20is%20still%20continuing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbEHLkhye5o%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbEHLkhye5o%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Western%20Naval%20Command%20(%40IN_WNC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIN_WNC%2Fstatus%2F1763897223622819922%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma's%20mother%2C%20Rama%20Kumari%2C%20suspects%20a%20cover-up%2C%20alleging%20that%20information%20is%20being%20concealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20400%20people%20on%20board%20the%20ship%20and%20only%20my%20son%20went%20missing.%20My%20prayers%20and%20demands%20are%20only%20that%20my%20son%20returns%20safe%20and%20sound%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%2C%20a%20maternal%20uncl