%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Liu%20Jianchao%2C%20Minister%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party's%20International%20Liaison%20Department%2C%20shakes%20hands%20with%20a%20French%20diplomat.%20Former%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Zhao%20Lijian%20speaks%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dc5bec90413ab8e1d6b7ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiu%20Jianchao%2C%20Minister%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party's%20International%20Liaison%20Department%2C%20shakes%20hands%20with%20a%20French%20diplomat.%20Former%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Zhao%20Lijian%20speaks%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3Cp%3EGao%20Jing%2FXinhua%20via%20Getty%20Images%20and%20GREG%20BAKER%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERecent%20shifts%20in%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20and%20tone%20have%20fueled%20speculation%20that%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%20may%20disappear.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20unlikely%20we'll%20see%20Beijing's%20aggressive%20ways%20go%20for%20good.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20a%20mistake%20to%20think%20that%20China%20has%20deliberately%20highlighted%20aggression%20as%20its%20default%20strategy%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20New%20York%2C%20veteran%20diplomat%20Liu%20Jianchao%20seemed%20to%20signal%20a%20reversal%20in%20how%20China%20wants%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20believe%20that%20there%20has%20always%20been%20a%20kind%20of%20'Wolf%20Warrior'%20diplomacy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Liu%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party's%20International%20Department%2C%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fevent%2Ffuture-china-and-china-us-relations-conversation-liu-jianchao%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECouncil%20of%20Foreign%20Relations%20talk%20on%20January%209.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20there's%20no%20talk%20about%20coming%20back%20to%20that%20diplomacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20words%20raised%20questions%20in%20the%20West.%20China%20has%20been%20known%20for%20its%20haughty%2C%20often%20hostile%20brand%20of%20diplomacy%2C%20known%20colloquially%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-wolf-warrior-diplomacy-backfires-uniting-rivals-dividing-at-home-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWolf%20Warrior%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20China%2C%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20also%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-foreign-minister-qin-gang-removed-disappearance-reason-experts-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20personnel%20changes%20to%20its%20foreign%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ejecting%20at%20least%20two%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomats.%20With%20its%20post-COVID%20economy%20struggling%20to%20get%20back%20on%20its%20feet%2C%20was%20Beijing%20sunsetting%20its%20aggressive%20ways%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20unlikely%2C%20even%20if%20China's%20been%20adopting%20a%20friendlier%20tone%2C%20four%20experts%20on%20the%20country's%20foreign%20relations%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221801%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Liu%20Jianchao%20(fourth%20from%20right)%2C%20attending%20a%20meeting%20with%20US%20State%20Secretary%20Antony%20Blinken%20in%20January.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e17e0c6080194819fb726e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221351%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiu%20Jianchao%20(third%20from%20right)%2C%20attending%20a%20meeting%20with%20US%20State%20Secretary%20Antony%20Blinken%20in%20January.%3Cp%3EROBERTO%20SCHMIDT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20misconception%20%E2%80%94%20and%20often%20a%20Western%20one%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Beijing%20has%20outlined%20a%20specific%20strategy%20to%20squabble%20and%20demean%20adversaries%20on%20the%20public%20stage%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aggressive%20style%20of%20diplomacy%20that%20the%20PRC%20sometimes%20undertakes%20is%20a%20tool%2C%20not%20an%20ideology%2C%20belief%2C%20or%20doctrine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ian%20Ja%20Chong%2C%20who%20teaches%20about%20Chinese%20foreign%20policy%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20pulls%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-wolf-warrior-diplomacy-has-come-to-wall-street-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20whenever%20it%20feels%20the%20need%20to%2C%20sometimes%20to%20intimidate%20smaller%20countries%2C%20but%20often%20says%20its%20behavior%20is%20righteous%20anger%20instead%20of%20a%20bullying%20tactic%2C%20Chong%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENamed%20for%20the%20nationalistic%202017%20Chinese%20film%20%26quot%3BWolf%20Warrior%202%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20term%20has%20come%20to%20encompass%20the%20litany%20of%20insults%20and%20wild%20claims%20made%20by%20Chinese%20diplomats%20in%20their%20defense%20of%20Beijing's%20interests.%20In%20one%20infamous%20example%20from%202020%2C%20Chinese%20spokesperson%20Zhao%20Lijian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F11%2F30%2Faustralia%2Faustralia-china-twitter-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%20a%20photo%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20showed%20a%20soldier%20about%20to%20slit%20a%20child's%20throat%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Australian%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShocked%20by%20the%20murder%20of%20Afghan%20civilians%20%26amp%3B%20prisoners%20by%20Australian%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhao%20wrote.%20The%20manipulated%20image%20stunned%20Australian%20leaders%2C%20who%20condemned%20the%20post%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20image%20and%20a%20terrible%20slur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224827%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesman%20Zhao%20Lijian%20attends%20a%20news%20conference%20on%20December%2020%2C%202021%20in%20Beijing%2C%20China.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e17ecece7f1785b2e52c13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223218%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesman%20Zhao%20Lijian%20would%20later%20be%20reassigned%20as%20deputy%20head%20of%20an%20ocean%20affairs%20bureau%2C%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20demotion.%20The%20move%20has%20also%20fueled%20speculation%20about%20the%20end%20of%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20more%20about%20the%20home%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomat's%20specific%20behaviors%20and%20level%20of%20aggression%20are%20unlikely%20to%20come%20at%20the%20direct%20instruction%20of%20their%20superiors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20it%20stems%20from%20an%20expectation%20for%20diplomats%20to%20protect%20Beijing's%20image%20fiercely%2C%20said%20Stanley%20Rosen%2C%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20and%20international%20relations%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California's%20US-China%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20who's%20a%20diplomat%20for%20China%20who%20wants%20to%20be%20promoted%20cannot%20take%20the%20soft%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20be%20defending%20China%20at%20all%20times.%20So%20you'll%20get%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble%20and%20not%20get%20promoted%20if%20you%20seem%20to%20be%20too%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20foreigners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20a%20diplomat%20who%20gets%20too%20aggressive%20might%20be%20asked%20to%20tone%20it%20down%2C%20but%20would%20rarely%20be%20sacked%20or%20face%20severe%20consequences%2C%20Rosen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptions%20at%20home%20are%20