uot%3BAnti-Bengali%26quot%3B%20Attack%2C%20BJP's%20%26quot%3BGo%20To%20Sandeshkhali%26quot%3B%20Retort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20fielding%20Bhojpuri%20Singer%20Pawan%20Singh%20from%20Asansol%20seat%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20anti-Bengali%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20giving%20tickets%20to%20those%20%26quot%3Bwho%20speak%20ill%20of%20women%26quot%3B%2C%20however%2C%20BJP%20in%20its%20reply%20said%20that%20TMC%20leaders%20must%20visit%20Sandeshkhali%20before%20making%20such%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20Singh%20announced%20earlier%20today%20that%20he%20won't%20be%20contesting%20from%20the%20Asansol%20seat%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20TMC%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20came%20here%2C%20lectured%20on%20'Nari%20Shakti'%20and%20then%20gave%20a%20ticket%20to%20someone%20who%20has%20vilified%20Bengali%20women.%20That's%20the%20'Modi%20ki%20guarantee'.%20If%20you%20speak%20ill%20of%20Bengal%2C%20if%20you%20speak%20ill%20of%20women%2C%20we'll%20give%20you%20a%20ticket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20remarks%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Ajay%20Alok%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDerek%20O'Brien%20should%20go%20to%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20see%20the%20atrocities%20against%20women%20then%20he%20will%20release%20who%20is%20anti-Bengali.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Pawan%20Singh%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20contesting%20from%20the%20Asansol%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20however%2C%20he%20did%20not%20mention%20any%20specific%20reason%20for%20this%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20The%20party%20trusted%20me%20and%20declared%20me%20as