ntertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frajinikanth-shah-rukh-khan-salman-khan-bill-gates-celebs-dazzle-on-the-final-day-of-anant-ambani-and-radhika-merchants-pre-wedding-celebrations%2Farticleshow%2F108186123.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NASA%20space%20photo%20shows%20odd-looking%20sky%20holes%20near%20Florida%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satellite%20image%20showing%20the%20green%20waters%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20and%20circular%20clouds%20circled%20in%20red%20indicating%20Cavum%20clouds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e4ad79ce7f1785b2e5bfc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222005%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECavum%20clouds%20are%20an%20odd%20phenomenon%20that%20have%20been%20mistaken%20for%20flying%20saucers.%3Cp%3ENASA%20Earth%20Observatory%20image%20by%20Michala%20Garrison%2C%20using%20MODIS%20data%20from%20NASA%20EOSDIS%20LANCE%20and%20GIBS%2FWorldview%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20NASA%20satellite%20snapped%20a%20photo%20of%20giant%20ring-shaped%20clouds%20over%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20see%20this%20phenomenon%2C%20called%20cavum%20clouds%2C%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20in%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECavum%20clouds%20have%20a%20natural%20explanation%20but%20have%20been%20mistaken%20for%20aliens%20and%20other%20odd%20phenomena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20NASA's%20Terra%20satellite%20was%20zipping%20over%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20when%20one%20of%20its%20instruments%20snapped%20a%20photo%20of%20some%20odd-looking%20clouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clouds%20looked%20like%20someone%20had%20taken%20a%20hole%20punch%20to%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20unusual%20phenomenon%20isn't%20new.%20Researchers%20have%20been%20documenting%20it%20since%20the%201940s%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fearthobservatory.nasa.gov%2Fimages%2F152486%2Fmaking-sense-of-holes-in-the-clouds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENASA%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20until%20about%2015%20years%20ago%20that%20scientists%20finally%20found%20an%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20features%20are%20officially%20called%20cavum%20clouds%2C%20but%20are%20sometimes%20nicknamed%20hole-punch%20clouds%20or%20fallstreak%20holes.%20They're%20so%20big%20that%20you%20can%20see%20them%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20ground%2C%20they%20can%20look%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22an%20oval%20shaped%20cavum%20cloud%20as%20seen%20from%20the%20ground%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e4b0e2ce7f1785b2e5bfde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECavum%20cloud%20as%20seen%20from%20the%20ground.%3Cp%3Epr2is%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20wonder%20that%20people%20have%20mistaken%20them%20for%20flying%20saucers%20or%20other%20unusual%20phenomenon.%20They%20don't%20look%20like%20your%20average%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20they%20aren't%20your%20average%20cloud.%20If%20it%20weren't%20for%20human%20technology%2C%20cavum%20clouds%20would%20never%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20form%20when%20airplanes%20fly%20through%20banks%20of%20mid-level%20altocumulus%20clouds%20%E2%80%94%20clouds%20made%20of%20supercooled%20droplets%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20studies%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.ametsoc.org%2Fview%2Fjournals%2Fbams%2F91%2F6%2F2009bams2905_1.xml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%202010%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.1202851%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2011%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20NASA's%20Langley%20Research%20Center%20found%20in%202010%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20the%20more%20shallow%20the%20angle%20that%20the%20plane%20takes%20to%20pass%20through%20the%20clouds%2C%20the%20larger%20the%20cavum%20left%20behind%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20showed%20that%20any%20type%20of%20plane%20can%20produce%20cavum%20clouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENASA's%20Terra%20satellite%20captured%20photos%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bcluster%26quot%3B%20of%20cavum%20clouds%20near%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20Florida%20on%20January%2030.%20The%20more%20than%201%2C000%20flights%20per%20day%20coming%20from%20the%20Miami%20International%20Airport%20are%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20the%20phenomenon%2C%20according%20to%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Terra%20satellite%20is%20designed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fterra.nasa.gov%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20study%20changes%20in%20Earth's%20atmosphere%20and%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Researchers%20use%20data%20collected%20from%20the%20satellite%20to%20map%20the%20impact%20of%20human%20activity%20and%20natural%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-space-photo-shows-sky-holes-near-florida-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709495058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e4aea8ce7f1785b2e5bfd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-space-photo-shows-sky-holes-near-florida-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20sky%20holes%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20in%20space.%20They're%20called%20cavum%20clouds%20and%20have%20a%20scientific%20explanation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jorwig%40businessinsider.com%20(Jessica%20Orwig%2CKenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A146%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-space-photo-shows-sky-holes-near-florida-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Researchers%20just%20discovered%20a%20massive%20'jacuzzi%20bubbling%20with%20almost%20pure%20hydrogen'%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lucrative%20source%20of%20clean%20energy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bulqiz%C3%AB%20chromite%20mine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e4c438ce7f1785b2e5c0a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bulqiz%C3%AB%20chromite%20mine%20just%2025%20miles%20east%20of%20Albania's%20capital%20Tirana%20contains%20a%20massive%20reservoir%20of%20hydrogen.%3Cp%3EGENT%20SHKULLAKU%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20team%20of%20researchers%20recently%20discovered%20a%20massive%20reservoir%20of%20hydrogen%20in%20a%20mine%20in%20Albania.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20concentrations%20of%20hydrogen%20are%20so%20high%20that%20it%20has%20caused%20explosions%20and%20killed%20miners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20reservoir%20could%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhydrogen-energy-help-climate-crisis-but-still-hurdles-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20source%20of%20clean%20hydrogen%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-hydrogen-fuel-industry-explainer-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHydrogen%20is%20becoming%20a%20favorable%20alternative%20to%20fossil%20fuels%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20doesn't%20release%20carbon%20into%20the%20environment%20when%20burned.%20The%20downside%20is%20that%20generating%20it%20has%20long%20been%20an%20energy-intensive%20business%20that%20emits%20greenhouse%20gasses%20that%20warm%20the%20planet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20recently%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20uncovered%20a%20massive%20reservoir%20of%20hydrogen%20buried%20in%20a%20mine%20in%20Albania%20that%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20source%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-hydrogen-france-clean-energy-climate-change-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eclean%2C%20hydrogen%20energy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reservoir%20%E2%80%94%20located%20in%20the%20Bulqiz%C3%AB%20chromite%20mine%20just%2025%20miles%20east%20of%20Albania's%20capital%2C%20Tirana%20%E2%80%94%20vents%20at%20least%20200%20tons%20of%20H2%20gas%20per%20year%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.adk9099%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereport%2C%20published%20last%20month%20in%20the%20journal%20Science%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20reported%20that%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20recorded%20flow%20rates%20of%20H2%C2%A0%20to%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20have%20observed%20deep%20in%20the%20mine%20is%20another%20dimension%2C%26quot%3B%20Laurent%20Truche%2C%20the%20study's%20lead%20author%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livescience.com%2Fplanet-earth%2Fenergy%2Fmassive-hydrogen-reservoir-discovered-beneath-an-albanian-mine-could-be-an-untapped-source-of-clean-energy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Live%20Science.%20The%20reservoir%20%26quot%3Bturns%20a%20draining%20pool%20inside%20a%20mine%20gallery%20into%20a%20breathtaking%2030-square-meter%20%5B323%20square%20feet%5D%20jacuzzi%20bubbling%20with%20almost%20pure%20hydrogen.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20hydrogen%20is%20also%20a%20highly%20flammable%20gas%2C%20and%20the%20high%20concentrations%20within%20the%20mine%20have%20reportedly%20caused%20three%20explosions%20that%20have%20killed%20four%20miners%20and%20injured%20several%20others%20since%202011%2C%20according%20to%20Live%20Science.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20hydrogen%20in%20the%20mine%20can%20be%20safely%20harnessed%2C%20the%20researchers%20believe%20it%20could%20be%20a%20key%20energy%20source.%20And%20while%20large%2C%20natural%20reservoirs%20of%20hydrogen%20similar%20to%20this%20are%20rare%2C%20the%20researchers%20note%20that%20places%20with%20similar%20geology%20may%20be%20good%20targets%20for%20locating%20other%20sources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20comes%20just%20months%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20announced%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhydrogen-tax-credit-plan-biden-administration-details-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einitiative%20to%20pour%20%247%20billion%20into%20seven%20hydrogen%20hubs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20in%20regions%20including%20the%20Gulf%20Coast%2C%20Pacific%20Northwest%2C%20and%20Appalachia.%20One%20of%20the%20initiative's%20goals%20is%20for%20the%20hubs%20to%20produce%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20three%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20clean%20hydrogen%20per%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20about%20one-third%20of%20the%202030%20US%20clean%20hydrogen%20production%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-discover-albanian-mine-could-be-hydrogen-source-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709494394000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e4c46a90413ab8e1d8ab11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-discover-albanian-mine-could-be-hydrogen-source-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20a%20massive%20reservoir%20of%20hydrogen%20buried%20deep%20within%20an%20Albanian%20mine%20that%20could%20be%20a%20key%20source%20of%20clean%20energy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40insider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-discover-albanian-mine-could-be-hydrogen-source-20