is%20Response%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResponding%20sharply%20to%20a%20question%20whether%20%26quot%3BIndia%20was%20being%20a%20bully%20in%20the%20region%26quot%3B%20(sub-continent%20and%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region)%2C%20at%20a%20book%20launch%20event%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20'big%20bullies'%20don't%20provide%20USD%204.5%20billion%20in%20aid%20when%20neighbours%20are%20in%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20change%20today%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20world%20is%20what%20has%20happened%20between%20India%20and%20its%20neighbours.%20When%20you%20say%20India%20is%20perceived%20as%20a%20big%20bully%2C%20you%20know%2C%20big%20bullies%20don't%20provide%20four%20and%20a%20half%20billion%20dollars%20when%20the%20neighbours%20are%20in%20trouble.%20Big%20bullies%20don't%20supply%20vaccines%20to%20other%20countries%20when%20COVID%20is%20on%20or%20make%20exceptions%20to%20their%20own%20rules%20to%20respond%20to%20food%20demands%20or%20fuel%20demands%20or%20fertilizer%20demands%20because%20some%20war%20in%20some%20other%20part%20of%20the%20world%20has%20complicated%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20at%20the%20event%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20clip%20of%20Mr%20Jaishankar's%20response%20to%20the%20'barb'%20was%20widely%20shared%20across%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20also%20have%20to%20look%20today%20at%20actually%20what%20is%20changed%20between%20India%20and%20its%20neighbours.%20Certainly%2C%20with%20Bangladesh%20and%20Nepal%2C%20I%20mean%20today%20you%20have%20a%20power%20grid%2C%20you%20have%20roads%20which%20didn't%20exist%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20you%20have%20railways%20which%20didn't%20exist%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20there's%20usage%20of%20waterways.%20Indian%20businesses%20use%20ports%20of%20Bangladesh%20on%20a%20national%20treatment%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20work%20undertaken%20to%20enhance%20and%20improve%20connectivity%20between%20India%20and%20its%20neighbouring%20countries%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20trade%2C%20investments%20and%20travel%20with%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Maldives%20have%20seen%20a%20sharp%20uptick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20at%20the%20connectivity%2C%20just%20the%20volume%20of%20people%20moving%20up%20and%20down%2C%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20trade%20which%20is%20there%2C%20the%20investments%20which%20are%20there%2C%20it's%20actually%20a%20very%2C%20very%20good%20story%20to%20tell.%20Not%20just%20with%20Nepal%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20as%20well%2C%20I%20would%20say%20even%20with%20Maldives%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20stated%20at%20the%20book%20launch%20event%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20Bhutan...I%20mean%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20miss%20them%20out%20because%20they%20have%20just%20been%20consistently%20strong%20partners.%20So%20our%20problem%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20very%20honestly%2C%20is%20in%20respect%20to%20one%20country.%20And%20in%20diplomacy%2C%20you%20always%20hold%20out%20hopes%20that%2C%20yes%2C%20okay%2C%20keep%20at%20it%2C%20and%20who%20knows%20one%20day%20what%20the%20future%20holds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20it%20was%20essential%20for%20an%20'average%20person'%20to%20actively%20engage%20with%20foreign%20policy%20matters%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCertainly%2C%20all%20Indians%20need%20to%20take%20more%20interest%20in%20foreign%20policy.%20it%20is%20very%20common%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20there%20is%20a%20belief%20that%20foreign%20policy%20is%20something%20complicated%2C%20esoteric%2C%20that%20should%20be%20left%20to%20certain%20people%20to%20deal%20with...which%20is%20not%20entirely%20without%20some%20justification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...But%2C%20to%20me%2C%20a%20number%20of%20events%20happened%2