d%20five-drawer%20dresser%20in%20my%20closet%2C%20and%20I%20finally%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20enough%20storage%20in%20my%20bedroom.%20I%20love%20my%20current%20setup%20of%20The%20Dresser%2C%20but%20I%20also%20love%20that%20I%20can%20switch%20things%20up%20if%20I%20move%20to%20a%20larger%20space%20or%20use%20it%20in%20another%20part%20of%20my%20home.%20I%20already%20have%20ideas%20about%20potentially%20using%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20drawers%20as%20underbed%20storage.%20The%20drawers%20would%20likely%20fit%20under%20beds%20with%2010%20inches%20of%20clearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EStorage%20Capacity%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Folded%20leggings%20and%20rolled%20shorts%20inside%20The%20Dresser%20drawer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1f85fce7f1785b2e554a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20drawers%20are%205%26quot%3B%20deep.%20I%20maximize%20space%20by%20rolling%20pants%20and%20leggings%20to%20fit%2025-30%20pieces.%3Cp%3EPauline%20Lacsamana%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20drawer%20is%20about%205%20inches%20tall%20and%2015%20inches%20deep%2C%20making%20The%20Dresser%20on%20the%20smaller%20side%20compared%20to%20other%20dressers%2C%20but%20the%20drawers%20are%20spacious%20enough%20to%20fit%20my%20storage%20needs.%20I%20have%20more%20space%20in%20The%20Dresser%20than%20any%20nightstand%20I've%20ever%20had.%20It%20houses%20all%20my%20essentials%20and%20more%2C%20including%20extra%20toothpaste%2C%20my%20hair%20dryer%2C%20and%20protein%20shakes%20(yes%2C%20there's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20everything%20because%20there's%20that%20much%20extra%20room).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dresser%20in%20my%20closet%20has%20made%20the%20most%20difference%20when%20organizing%20my%20clothes.%20It's%20truly%20been%20a%20journey%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20good%20closet%20storage%20system.%20Before%20getting%20The%20Dresser%2C%20I%20tried%20everything%20from%20wire%20cubes%20to%20hanging%20storage%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20my%20closet%20space.%20With%20The%20Dresser%2C%20I%20can%20keep%20my%20clothes%20in%20check%20and%20hang%20clothes%20to%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20drawers%20and%20even%20shorter%20pieces%2C%20like%20t-shirts%20or%20tank%20tops%2C%20above%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20drawers%20by%20folding%20lighter%20clothes.%20In%20one%20drawer%2C%20I%20can%20fit%20around%2024%20to%2030%20T-shirts.%20In%20another%2C%20I%20can%20fit%2010%20to%2014%20rolled%20shorts%20and%20about%2014%20pairs%20of%20leggings.%20Since%20I%20have%20many%20bulkier%20items%2C%20like%20sweatpants%20and%20sweatshirts%2C%20I%20stack%20them%20on%20a%20shelf%20with%20dividers%20rather%20than%20inside%20The%20Dresser.%20But%20if%20you%20plan%20on%20storing%20your%20sweatpants%20there%2C%20you%20can%20likely%20fit%20around%20six%20pairs%20of%20sweatpants%20(or%20more%20depending%20on%20how%20you%20fold%20them)%2C%20with%20a%20few%20inches%20to%20spare%20for%20rolled%20or%20smaller%20pieces%20of%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESustainability%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20design%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20versatility%2C%20Thuma's%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20can%20go%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20what%20The%20Dresser%20is%20made%20of.%20It's%20crafted%20by%20100%25%20repurposed%20solid%20wood%20that%20looks%20beautiful%20and%20feels%20durable.%20It's%20also%20GREENGUARD%20Gold%20Certified%2C%20meaning%20it's%20gone%20through%20thorough%20testing%20and%20is%20certified%20to%20have%20low%20chemical%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20potential%20setbacks%20of%20The%20Dresser%20are%20the%20price%20and%20the%20packaging.%20It%20can%20cost%20anywhere%20between%20%24790%20and%20%243%2C495%20depending%20on%20which%20configuration%20you%20choose.%20With%20the%20quality%2C%20design%2C%20and%20versatility%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20the%20investment%2C%20but%20realistically%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20most%20budget-friendly%20dresser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20for%20the%20packaging.%20I%20appreciate%20the%20commitment%20to%20using%20more%20eco-friendly%20options.%20However%2C%20breaking%20down%20the%20cardboard%20took%20me%20days%2C%20and%20recycling%20took%20weeks.%20If%20you%20have%20limited%20space%2C%20keep%20the%20packaging%20aftermath%20in%20mind%2C%20as%20the%20bigger%20the%20configuration%20you%20get%2C%20the%20more%20cardboard%20you'll%20have%20to%20recycle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20like%20minimalist%20design%20and%20versatile%20storage%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20getting%20Thuma's%20The%20Dresser.%20After%20living%20with%20The%20Dresser%20for%20the%20last%20year%2C%20I%20confidently%20believe%20this%20modular%20design%20is%20built%20to%20last%20and%20is%20a%20special%20piece%20that%20upgrades%20everyday%20living.%20It's%20on%20the%20pricier%20side%2C%20but%20it's%20backed%20up%20by%20high-quality%20materials%20and%20a%20modular%20system%20that%20you%20can%20easily%20add%20to%20or%20rearrange%20as%20your%20needs%20and%20space%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fthuma-dresser-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709488801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1ebb36080194819fb8acd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fthuma-dresser-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thuma's%20The%20Dresser%20is%20a%20minimalist%20and%20modular%20dresser%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20assemble.%20It's%20a%20great-looking%20piece%20designed%20to%20grow%20w