e%20you%20fielded%20a%20candidate%20who%20was%20beaten%20up%20by%20his%20own%20cadre%20in%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20yesterday%20(Saturday)%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20named%20a%20candidate%20who%20is%20not%20liked%20by%20his%20own%20party%20members.%20They%20can%20put%20allegations%20against%20us%20but%20people%20will%20give%20them%20a%20reply%20in%20the%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomnath%20Bharti%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20candidate%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency%2C%20also%20demanded%20that%20Swaraj%20and%20the%20BJP%20should%20%26quot%3Bapologise%20for%20such%20a%20blunder%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20Atishi%20also%20spoke%20about%20outgoing%20BJP%20MP%20Harsh%20Vardhan's%20decision%20to%20bow%20out%20of%20electoral%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vardhan%20is%20known%20for%20his%20honesty%20and%20hard%20work%20for%20the%20country%2C%20the%20people%20of%20his%20parliamentary%20constituency%20and%20his%20assembly%20constituency%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20always%20raised%20issues%20of%20public%20interest%20and%20spoke%20for%20them.%20I%20think%20it%20has%20become%20very%20clear%20that%20just%20as%20he%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20position%20of%20health%20minister%20at%20one%20time%20for%20raising%20some%20issues%2C%20today%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20perhaps%20his%20ticket%20has%20been%20cut%20due%20to%20his%20honesty%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarring%20North%20East%20Delhi%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20named%20Manoj%20Tiwari%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20it%20has%20fielded%20new%20faces%20from%20four%20constituencies%20--%20New%20Delhi%20(Swaraj)%2C%20West%20Delhi%20(Kamaljeet%20Sehrawat)%2C%20South%20Delhi%20(Ramvir%20Singh%20Bidhuri)%20and%20Chandni%20Chowk%20(Praveen%20Khandelwal).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20name%20its%20candidates%20for%20East%20Delhi%20--%20where%20MP%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20said