2210-Day%20Yatra%20and%20a%20Mega%20Rally%3A%20Tejashwi%20Attempts%20to%20Go%20Beyond%20Muslim-Yadav%20Formula%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03192044%2FGHP5gulWQAIOIL_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPatna%20(Bihar)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20a%20barometer%20to%20measure%20the%20political%20clout%2C%20on%20Sunday%20witnessed%20a%20substantial%20crowd%20in%20a%20mega%20rally%20organised%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahagathbandhan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20the%20grand%20alliance%20which%20consists%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20Congress%2C%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20and%20other%20left%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20crowd%20shouted%20and%20clapped%20at%20every%20sentence%20uttered%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYadav%20took%20credit%20for%20providing%20employment%20to%20the%20youth%20during%20his%20short%20tenure%20as%20deputy%20chief%20and%20said%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20among%20youths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20BJP%20is%20his%20core%20political%20rival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERJD%20supremo%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20Misa%20Bharti%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20leader%20Dipankar%20Bhattacharya%20and%20other%20leaders%20were%20present%20in%20the%20rally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rally%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%2010-day%20long%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Yatra%20of%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20which%20started%20on%20February%2020%2C%20weeks%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ditched%20the%20mahagathbandhan%20and%20went%20back%20to%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20yatra%20covered%20a%20distance%20of%203%2C500%20kilometres%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewitnessing%20an%20unexpectedly%20large%20crowd.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20yatra%2C%20Tejashwi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20focused%20on%20employment%20and%20said%20that%20RJD%20is%20the%20party%20for%20all.%20He%20even%20moved%20beyond%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20slogan%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20talked%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esamajik%20nyay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(social%20justice)%20along%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Earthik%20nyay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(economic%20justice).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEconomic%20development%20along%20with%20social%20justice%20slogan%20was%20coined%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20soon%20after%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%20in%202005.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDecoding%20the%20crowd%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERJD%20sources%20said%20that%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20yatra%20attracted%20a%20huge%20crowd%2C%20it%20was%20taken%20through%20those%20areas%20that%20are%20considered%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20strongholds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20local%20RJD%20MLAs%20were%20instructed%20to%20bring%20people%20from%20their%20areas%20on%20the%20yatra%20route.%20The%20other%20alliance%20partners%20of%20the%20mahagathbandhan%2C%20like%20CPI-ML%20workers%2C%20were%20also%20tasked%20to%20gather%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20journalists%20who%20covered%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20said%20that%20the%20crowd%20primarily%20consisted%20of%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20core%20supporters%20%E2%80%93%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims.%20However%2C%20people%20from%20other%20castes%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20yatra%2C%20but%20their%20number%20was%20relatively%20less.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20journalist%20who%20covered%20the%20yatra%20in%20Nalanda%20said%20that%20there%20were%20mostly%20youngsters%20in%20the%20rally%2C%20and%20they%20were%20mostly%20from%20Yadav%20and%20Muslim%20communities.%20Other%20castes%20also%20joined%20the%20rally%20but%20in%20lesser%20numbers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYouths%20were%20jubilant%20and%20it%20seems%20they%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20Tejashwi%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20can%20address%20their%20aspirations.%20He%20gave%20jobs%20to%20youths%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20continuously%20talking%20about%20jobs%20as%20an%20opposition%20leader%20has%20worked%20in%20his%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yatra-bihar-bjp-desperate-to-change-headlines%5C%22%3EThreatened%20by%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Yatra%2C%20BJP%20Desperate%20to%20Change%20Headlines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnemployment%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20for%20the%20youth%20and%20Tejashwi%20has%20created%20aspiration%20among%20them.%20Even%20in%20the%202020%20elections%2C%20he%20had%20established%20the%20employment%20narrative%2C%20due%20to%20which%20no%20other%20narrative%20worked%2C%20and%20other%20parties%20also%20had%20to%20talk%20about%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20political%20analyst%20Mahendra%20Suman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTejashwi%20has%20given%20an%20initial%20blow%20to%20BJP%20and%20JDU%20by%20gathering%20a%20huge%20crowd%2C%20but%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20draw%20any%20conclusions%20from%20this%20crowd%20because%20a%20lot%20depends%20on%20what%20he%20does%20next%20after%20this%20yatra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatna-based%20journalist%20Amarnath%20Tiwary%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20remote%20villages%2C%20people%20do%20gather%20in%20large%20numbers%20if%20a%20political%20leader%20makes%20a%20visit.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20this%20crowd%20will%20convert%20into%20votes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20go%20beyond%20M-Y%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20yatra%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20mega%20rally%2C%20Tejashwi%20reiterated%20that%20RJD%20is%20the%20party%20of%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20not%20only%20of%20Yadav%20and%20Muslim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRJD%20is%20not%20only%20the%20party%20of%20MY%20(Muslims%20and%20Yadavs)%20but%20also%20the%20party%20of%20BAAP.%20B%20means%20Bahujan%2C%20A%20means%20agra%20(forward%20classes)%2C%20A%20means%20adhi%20awaadi%20(women)%20P%20means%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20mega%20rally%20in%20Gandhi%20Maidan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20full%20form%20of%20RJD%20is%20Rights%2C%20Jobs%20and%20Development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETejashwi%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20make%20RJD%20a%20party%20of%20all%20castes%20and%20creeds%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20In%20the%202020%20Bihar%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20he%20was%20the%20campaigner%20of%20mahagathbandhan%20and%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20Tejashwi%20had%20said%20that%20RJD%20is%20the%20party%20of%20%E2%80%98A%20to%20Z.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20political%20analysts%20and%20journalists%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98A%20to%20Z%E2%80%99%20combination%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20see%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20in%20elections%2C%20you%20will%20not%20find%20that%20different%20caste%20groups%20are%20proportionately%20represented%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Patna-based%20journalist%20Amarnath%20Tiwary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuman%20said%20that%20if%C2%A0%20Tejashwi%20talks%20about%20social%20justice%2C%20it%20should%20be%20reflected%20in%20his%20decisions.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20social%20justice%20as%20rhetoric%20will%20not%20help.%20They%20must%20put%20forward%20a%20clear%20blueprint%20for%20this.%20And%20he%20should%20also%20realise%20that%20social%20justice%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20empowering%20just%20one%20dominant%20caste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Patna-based%20journalist%20Santosh%20Singh%20says%20that%20making%20RJD%20acceptable%20to%20all%20parties%20is%20a%20process%20in%20progress%20but%20notes%20that%20there%20are%20challenges%20to%20attracting%20caste-neutral%20youths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20he%20is%20smart%20in%20talking%20about%20jobs%20for%20youths%20%E2%80%93%20caste-neutral%20issue.%20Tejashwi%20has%20started%20seeing%20youths%20as%20a%20possible%20constituency.%20This%20is%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20well.%20He%20is%20getting%20traction%20among%20youths%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamakant%20Chandan%2C%20a%20Patna%20based%20journalist%2C%20believes%20that%20upper%20castes%20are%20slowly%20turning%20to%20RJD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTejashwi%20is%20targeting%20upper%20caste%20votes%20but%20also%20keeping%20grip%20on%20his%20core%20vote%20bank%20of%20M-Y%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUpper%20castes%E2%80%99%20viewpoint%20about%20RJD%20is%20changing.%20Upper%20castes%20may%20not%20be%20turning%20towards%20RJD%20in%20huge%20numbers%20but%20they%20are%20not%20hating%20the%20party%20as%20they%20were%20doing%20earlier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A