rocess%20smoother%20and%20more%20inclusive%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20some%20major%20concerns%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20public%20discussion%20seems%20to%20have%20happened%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20despite%20this%20idea%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dnaindia.com%2Fanalysis%2Feditorial_pune-edit-polling-booths-in-housing-societies-are-welcome_1634537%5C%22%3Epitched%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20early%20as%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESegregation%20and%20exclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20proposal%20will%20help%20some%20people%20experience%20a%20less%20crowded%20polling%20station%20at%20their%20doorstep.%20However%2C%20it%20may%20cater%20exclusively%20to%20a%20certain%20class%20of%20society%2C%20leaving%20out%20the%20rest%20from%20accruing%20its%20direct%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20intention%20had%20been%20to%20make%20the%20polling%20process%20smoother%2C%20then%20densely%20populated%20neighbourhoods%2C%20slums%2C%20squatter%20colonies%2C%20and%20densely%20populated%20urban%20ghettos%20should%20have%20been%20the%20prime%20target%20of%20this%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpatna-news%2Fset-up-booths-in-high-rises-to-boost-urban-voter-turnout-eci-tells-ceos-101695828986261.html%5C%22%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20ECI%20told%20Chief%20Election%20Officers%20that%20a%20similar%20exercise%20should%20be%20also%20carried%20out%20in%20slum%20clusters%20in%20urban%20areas.%20However%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20only%20the%20housing%20societies%20were%20considered%20when%20the%20surveys%20and%20public%20consultations%20were%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20remarkable%20disconnect%20already%20exists%20between%20the%20financially%20solvent%20urban%20upper-middle%20class%20and%20the%20other%20sections%20of%20society.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20infrastructures%20in%20gated%20communities%2C%20air%20conditioned%20malls%20and%20cinema%20halls%2C%20and%20high-end%20private%20vehicles%20have%20been%20produced%20to%20bolster%20this%20disconnect.%20The%20common%20marketplaces%20from%20where%20people%20across%20classes%20used%20to%20buy%20daily%20groceries%20and%20other%20necessities%20have%20probably%20been%20the%20last%20significant%20demise%20of%20shared%20public%20spaces%2C%20after%20the%20demise%20of%20shared%20public%20transport%20and%20shared%20government%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20or%20parks%20and%20playgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20urban%20upper-middle%20classes%20and%20their%20children%20practically%20share%20no%20public%20space%20for%20their%20daily%20survival%20with%20other%20social%20sections%2Fclasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20they%20see%20sharing%20space%20equally%20with%20the%20poorer%20classes%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fstreets-in-motion%2F2D42F4BF0D2086A1DBB254A5120ACB42%5C%22%3Eobstruction%20to%20a%20smooth%20and%20comfortable%20urban%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20installation%20of%20polling%20stations%20within%20gated%20communities%20epitomises%20the%20ongoing%20trend%20of%20gentrification%20and%20urban%20segregation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fthe-contradictions-of-the-urban-in-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Contradictions%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Urban%E2%80%99%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsolidation%20of%20a%20class-based%20vote%20bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20measure%20may%20also%20generate%20a%20middle%20and%20upper-middle-class%20vote%20bank%20in%20urban%20India%2C%20influencing%20outcomes%20in%20smaller%20municipal%20elections.%20A%20massive%20gap%20in%20municipal%20services%20exists%20between%20affluent%20neighbourhoods%20and%20their%20adjacent%20slums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20middle%20class%20knows%20how%20to%20work%20through%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20political%20system%20beyond%20the%20electoral%20calculus.%20Usually%2C%20they%20retain%20their%20privilege%20through%20social%20networks%20among%20government%20functionaries.%20The%20new%20measure%20will%20be%20an%20additional%20boost%20to%20their%20social%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20empowerment%20of%20the%20Resident%20Welfare%20Associations%20(RWA)%20might%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20adjacent%20slums%20and%20lower-class%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20RWAs%20are%20often%20seen%20to%20be%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20involved%20in%20squatter%20colony%20eviction%20drives%2C%20land%20grabs%2C%20and%20privatisation%20of%20public%20parks%20and%20streets.%20Establishing%20polling%20booths%20in%20gated%20communities%20could%20further%20empower%20these%20RWAs%20to%20privatise%20the%20election%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20this%20move%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20address%20a%20long-standing%20self-perception%20of%20the%20urban%20middle%20class%20as%20the%20victim%20of%20populist%20politics.%20It%20is%20a%20common%20sentiment%20among%20the%20members%20of%20this%20class%20that%20taxpayers%E2%80%99%20money%20goes%20into%20government%20doles%20for%20the%20less%20privileged%20classes.%20They%20tend%20to%20believe%20that%20their%20numerical%20weakness%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20rest%20makes%20them%20susceptible%20to%20the%20violation%20of%20what%20%E2%80%98belongs%E2%80%99%20to%20them%20%E2%80%98rightfully.%E2%80%99%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20grossly%20incorrect%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20obvious%20economic%20clout%2C%20they%20also%20enjoy%20primacy%20in%20discourse%20and%20policymaking%20and%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20state%20via%20powerful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcup.columbia.edu%2Fbook%2Fthe-politics-of-the-governed%2F9780231130639%5C%22%3Ecivil%20social%20associations%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20social%20contact%20with%20elite%20regime%20functionaries%20and%20the%20judiciary.%20The%20move%20may%20have%20been%20designed%20to%20give%20this%20class%20an%20electoral%20prominence%20as%20well%2C%20which%20had%20eroded%20steadily%20since%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContradiction%20with%20the%20existing%20ECI%20guidelines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20concern%20is%20the%20neutrality%20and%20sanctity%20of%20the%20election%20process%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20neutrality%20of%20the%20space%20of%20the%20polling%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20government%20premises%20have%20been%20converted%20into%20polling%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Feci-backend%2Fpublic%2Fapi%2Fdownload%3Furl%3DLMAhAK6sOPBp%252FNFF0iRfXbEB1EVSLT41NNLRjYNJJP1KivrUxbfqkDatmHy12e%252FzVx8fLfn2ReU7TfrqYobgIhX2hcHezql%252B6nnk2%252FeqbrIw7XG4Ymo1b5MUat9bvOSUeplspufSrYrPT3q0YbDQfZyuRDbsLdMoGfiLASl33aHkYQNivX5P6biD0TueLJ0i%5C%22%3EECI%20Handbook%20for%20Returning%20Officer%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20possible%2C%20polling%20stations%20should%20be%20located%20in%20schools%20(Government%20or%20aided)%20and%20other%20Government%20or%20Semi-Government%20institutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%20further%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20location%20of%20the%20polling%20stations%20in%20private%20buildings%20or%20premises%20should%20generally%20be%20avoided.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20conditions%20saying%20that%20if%20taking%20a%20private%20premise%20becomes%20%E2%80%98unavoidable%E2%80%99%2C%20then%20%E2%80%9Cno%20watch%20and%20ward%20or%20other%20personnel%20connected%20with%20the%20owner%2C%20whether%20armed%20or%20unarmed%2C%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20either%20at%20the%20polling%20station%20or%20within%20a%20radius%20of%20two%20hundred%20meters%20around%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20after%20nominations%20are%20filed%2C%20it%20should%20be%20ensured%20that%20the%20owner%20of%20such%20a%20private%20building%20is%20not%20a%20contesting%20candidate%20or%20a%20known%20sympathizer%20or%20worker%20of%20any%20of%20the%20candidates%20at%20the%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20maintain%20neutrality%2C%20it%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20polling%20station%20should%20be%20located%20in%20police%20stations%2C%20hospitals%2C%20temples%20or%20places%20with%20religious%20significance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20to%20offset%20the%20power%20of%20the%20forward%20castes%20at%20the%20local%20levels%2C%20the%20Handbook%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20separate%20polling%20stations%20have%20been%20set%20up%20in%20areas%2C%20electors%20of%20which%20are%20predominantly%20SC%2FST%20and%20other%20weaker%20sections%20of%20the%20society%2C%20and%20that%20no%20such%20area%20has%20been%20either%20left%20out%20or%20linked%20with%20areas%20where%20electors%20predominantly%20belong%20to%20forward%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20argue%20that%20the%20concern%20of%20a%20substantial%20democracy%20cannot%20divert%20from%20ensuring%20equal%20political%20rights%20for%20the%20marginalised%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20important%20concern%20for%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20at%20least%20theoretically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20move%20to%20set%20up%20polling%20stations%20in%20housing%20societies%20tilts%20the%20power%20balance%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20based%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20RWAs%20of%20high-rise%20and%20housing%20societies%20are%20benign%20institutions%20of%20citizens%2C%20which%20is%20a%20gross%20misassessment%20of%20how%20RWAs%20are%20situated%20within%20the%20residents%20of%20that%20apartment%20complex%20and%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ingentaconnect.com%2Fcontent%2Fpaaf%2Fpaaf%2F2013%2F00000086%2F00000004%2Fart00005%5C%22%3ESeveral%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1002%2F9781118295823.ch7%5C%22%3Eethnographic%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1111%2Fj.1468-2427.2011.01043.x%5C%22%3Eacademic%3C%2Fa%3E%20accounts%20of%20how%20the%20RWAs%20function%20in%20cities%20such%20as%20Delhi%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20often%2C%20the%20RWAs%20act%20as%20Hindu%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20organisations%20of%20the%20house%20owners%2C%20dictatorially%20regulating%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fthe-dictatorial-republic-of-rwas-the-other-big-problem-covid-created-for-india%2F524819%2F%5C%22%3Eintimate%20life%20of%20the%20inmates%20of%20the%20gated%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20the%20tenants%2C%20young%20adults%2C%20single%20women%2C%20homosexual%20couples%2C%20etc.%20Issues%20have%20been%20reported%20where%20RWAs%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2Findia%2F1028381%2Fnoida-mahagun-moderne-the-case-of-a-missing-maid-has-ignited-a-class-war-in-a-luxury-housing-complex-in-india%5C%22%3Ebrutal%20towards%20domestic%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20discriminatory%20towards%20delivery%20workers%20and%20other%20service-providing%20workers%20by%20stopping%20them%20from%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fblogs%2Fvoices%2Fsofa-to-lift-rwa-curbs-on-service-staff-smack-of-deep-rooted-bias%2F%3Fsource%3Dapp%26frmapp%3Dyes%5C%22%3Elifts%2C%20sofas%2C%20or%20other%20common%20places%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20many%20places%2C%20the%20RWAs%20fix%20the%20rent%20of%20the%20properties%20as%20well.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20tenants%20do%20not%20have%20similar%20collectives%20in%20these%20gated%20communities%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20uneven%20distribution%20of%20class%20power%20even%20within%20the%20communities.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20the%20influential%20members%20of%20the%20RWAs%20are%20members%20of%20dominant%20political%20parties%20of%20the%20locality%20and%20use%20RWAs%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findias-rwa-uncles-are-now-adding-to-the-intolerance-around-us%5C%22%3Epolitical%20motives%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20accepting%20these%20organisations%20as%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20contradicts%20the%20principle%20of%20neutrality%20that%20the%20prevailing%20electoral%20conventions%20and%20rules%20uphold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-simultaneous-polls-may-reduce-india-to-worlds-largest-democracy-only-in-name%5C%22%3EWhy%20Simultaneous%20Polls%20May%20Reduce%20India%20to%20%E2%80%98World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20Only%20in%20Name%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20a%20more%20inclusive%20electoral%20policy%20is%20easy%20to%20imagine%20and%20materialize.%20This%20could%20be%20achieved%20by%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20polling%20booths%20while%20adhering%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20aforementioned%20directive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrban%20India%20does%20not%20lack%20government%20or%20semi-government%20premises%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20colleges.%20These%20premises%20can%20be%20requisitioned%20to%20make%20the%20polling%20experience%20smooth.%20Each%20citizen%20of%20this%20country%20deserves%20such%20an%20experience%2C%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20exclusive%20to%20the%20upper-middle%20class%20living%20in%20high-rises%20and%20gated%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20vital%20to%20ensure%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpostal-ballot-votes-migrant-workers%5C%22%3Einter-state%20migrant%20labourers%20can%20vote%20via%20the%20postal%20ballot%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20constitute%20a%20vast%20section%20of%20the%20missing%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20the%20postal%20ballot%20provisions%2