ur-violence-cbi-files-charge-sheet-against-7-in-manipur-armoury-loot-case-5167167%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2Fcbi-files-charge-sheet-against-seven-in-bishnupur-weapon-looting-case-2919815%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20chargesheets%20filed%20in%20the%20court%20of%20Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20of%20Guwahati%20in%20Assam%2C%20had%20named%20the%20accused%20as%20Laishram%20Prem%20Singh%2C%20Khumukcham%20Dhiren%20alias%20Thapkpa%2C%20Moirangthem%20Anand%20Singh%2C%20Athokpam%20Kajit%20alias%20Kishorjit%2C%20Loukrakpam%20Michael%20Mangangcha%20alias%20Michael%2C%20Konthoujam%20Romojit%20Meitei%20alias%20Romojit%20and%20Keisham%20Johnson%20alias%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20transferred%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20on%20August%2024%20last%20year.%20The%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20so%20far%20transferred%2029%20cases%20to%20the%20CBI.%20As%20per%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20these%20cases%20are%20being%20tried%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20Assam%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20is%20one%20among%20several%20others%20related%20to%20the%20looting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20from%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley%20districts%20of%20Manipur%20during%20the%20ethnic%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Kangpokpi%20district%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-assembly-adopts-resolution-to-abrogate-soo-deal-with-kuki-outfits-101709217505619.html%5C%22%3Eis%20set%20to%20witness%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20shutdown%20on%20March%204%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20adoption%20of%20a%20resolution%20on%20February%2029.%20The%20resolution%20aims%20to%20abrogate%20the%20suspension%20of%20operation%20(SoO)%20