pg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20newsletter%20is%20part%20of%20an%20open%20archive%20of%20Girish%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20work%20conceived%20by%20Raghu%20and%20Chaitanya%20as%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20his%20wide%20legacy%20alive%20and%20in%20public%20view.%20Its%20curator%20is%20Harismita.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPadmavati%20(Pinty)%20Rao%20recalls%20an%20evening%20working%20on%20%3Cem%3EMalgudi%20Days%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20mid-1980s.%20She%20was%20winding%20down%20on%20set%20with%20Girish%20Karnad%20and%20Shankar%20Nag%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20Saturday%20night%2C%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20a%20rented%20cottage%20under%20a%20star-laden%20sky%E2%80%A6%20there%20was%20Girish%2C%20telling%20us%20the%20story%20of%20%3Cem%3ENagamandala%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20folktale%20that%20A.K.%20Ramanujan%20had%20told%20him%20and%20Kambar.%20Everything%20about%20that%20evening%20in%20my%20memory%20is%20surreal.%20He%20for%20some%20reason%20was%20standing%20while%20we%2C%20Shankar%20and%20I%2C%20sat%20on%20the%20steps%20with%20our%20folks%20from%20%5BMalgudi%20Days%5D.%20%E2%80%A6%20Girish%E2%80%99s%20voice%20pierced%20the%20night%20sky%20and%20prevailed%20over%20the%20sound%20of%20wild%20nocturnal%20life%20in%20Agumbe%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20discussions%20of%20rituals%2C%20reptiles%2C%20the%20paranormal%20and%20much%20else%20also%20followed.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20experienced%20a%20night%20sky%20like%20that%20ever%20after%2C%20layered%20with%20a%20timeless%20story%20in%20a%20voice%20and%20erudition%20as%20rich%20as%20his.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnad%20had%20heard%20two%20folktales%20from%20Ramanujan.%20The%20first%20was%20the%20tale%20of%20%3Cem%3EA%20Story%20and%20a%20Song%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20suppressed%20deep%20inside%20a%20woman%2C%20fighting%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20and%20be%20freed.%20The%20second%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Serpent%20Lover%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20about%20a%20woman%20with%20an%20uncaring%20husband%2