for%20the%20snake%20and%20the%20dog%20which%20were%20handled%20by%20puppeteers%20on%20a%20concealed%20catwalk.%20That%20was%20where%20they%20swung%20the%20lit%20lamps%20from%20%E2%80%94%20which%20had%20to%20have%20mustard%20oil%20so%20they%20would%20not%20go%20off%20in%20the%20wind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cast%20included%20B.%20Jayashri%2C%20Ramesh%20Bhat%2C%20and%20Shankar%20Nag%20himself.%20It%20was%20scored%20by%20C.%20Ashwath%2C%20with%20a%20spectacular%20song%2C%20%E2%80%9CMaayada%20Manada%20Bhara%E2%80%9D%20written%20by%20Gopal%20Vajpeyi.%20Listen%20to%20a%20rendition%20of%20the%20song%20by%20Pallavi%20MD%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fci3.googleusercontent.com%2Fmeips%2FADKq_NYuodSvGkCiQjEtAD16PM6XTMGkiNh50cdfXioKy-LB37Xr9t-nwTG2daFsVDxA5yoaOseP1bEC1LxlrEcK_N1FXGutjbw3usCWZTWaOmxoPh9CGuhXAal626Jwan4UENl7pw9wdGFIfYu7HafEV3qM-YQyafgtO5a1eNcQJ2eai3Cbh4vX5lJKGSELVZvLC1bjuu1LkJHUlFWyu_hXKuDd9yUnM6m0CS13HUc9OV4yJtOGqLqn4zRwyP72psSqRoN4ZC6oTcZueAAMeg27dCdXz6Q7Dp8usiO6vc9e8rajQ96nOPI81i9exA%3Ds0-d-e1-ft%23https%3A%2F%2Fsubstackcdn.com%2Fimage%2Ffetch%2Fw_1456%2Cc_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cq_auto%3Agood%2Cfl_progressive%3Asteep%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%252Fpublic%252Fimages%252F48aaa770-2fe0-4c7c-9525-9817e5fd82ec_1456x474.png%5C%22%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221456%5C%22%20data-bit%3D%5C%22iit%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22474%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShankar%20Nag%E2%80%99s%20Nagamandala%20(1989)%2C%20with%20Rani%20played%20by%20Pinty%20Rao%20(left%20and%20centre)%20and%20Arundathi%20Nag%20(right).%20Photo%3A%20Ranga%20Shankara.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20Delhi%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20Neelam%20Mansingh%20Chowdhry%20was%20creating%20a%20production%20in%20Punjabi%20that%20she%20would%20breathe%20life%20into%20again%20and%20again%20over%20the%20next%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaga%20Chhay