%20coloured%20lithographs%20of%20his%20original%20paintings%20for%20mass%20distribution.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20other%20lithographic%20presses%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20posters%20were%20made%20by%20prominent%20Indian%20painters%20of%20the%20time%2C%20including%20Varma%2C%20M.V.%20Dhurandhar%2C%20S.L.%20Haldankar%20and%20Raghuvir%20Mulgaonkar.%20Others%20are%20by%20artists%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20such%20as%20Victor%20Veevers%2C%20Kay%20Nixon%2C%20Dorothy%20Newsome%20and%20W.S.%20Bylitiplis%2C%20who%20were%20stationed%20in%20India%20during%20those%20days%20and%20had%20their%20paintings%20specifically%20designed%20for%20posters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20collectors%20go%20on%20an%20initial%20spree%20of%20collecting%20whatever%20they%20find%20interesting.%20As%20time%20goes%20by%2C%20they%20start%20researching%20on%20the%20techniques%2C%20companies%2C%20artists%2C%20styles%2C%20printers%20and%20their%20values.%20When%20the%20collection%20becomes%20large%2C%20one%20often%20tends%20to%20forget%20what%20one%20has%20acquired.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Thakral%20also%20has%20an%20enormous%20collection%20of%205%2C000%2C%20one-of-a-kind%2C%20original%20popular%20visual%20arts%20in%20the%20form%20of%20old%20calendars%2C%20posters%2C%20oleographs%20and%20prints.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20not%20to%20waste%20money%20on%20duplicates%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20catalogue%20them%2C%20so%20that%20one%20has%20a%20ready%20reckoner%20of%20what%20one%20has%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakral.%20The%20collection%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20catalogued%20and%20maintained%20under%20the%20Tarun%20Thakral%20Archival%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22h