ial%20resources%2C%20without%20any%20external%20support%20for%20its%20development.%20I%20reinvested%20the%20benefits%20to%20fuel%20its%20growth%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20slow%20but%20organic%20progression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20some%20of%20the%20unique%20experiences%20that%20a%20guest%20receives%20at%20the%20stay%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20activities%20to%20our%20guests%2C%20aimed%20at%20providing%20them%20with%20a%20comprehensive%20exploration%20of%20our%20culture%20and%20the%20chance%20to%20interact%20with%20members%20of%20the%20local%20community%2C%20all%20while%20ensuring%20fair%20supplementary%20income%20for%20them.%20These%20activities%20encompass%20various%20aspects%20of%20our%20heritage%20and%20traditions%2C%20without%20compromising%20on%20authenticity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuests%20can%20enjoy%20craft%20workshops%20including%20tie-dye%2C%20bangle%20making%2C%20pottery%2C%20Mandala%20drawing%2C%20and%20handmade%20recycled%20paper%2C%20along%20with%20cookery%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20guided%20excursions%20to%20explore%20Shekhawati%E2%80%99s%20unique%20heritage%2C%20countryside%20outings%20such%20as%20bicycle%20tours%20and%20camel%20cart%20strolls%2C%20and%20live%20music%20programs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainability%20at%20its%20very%20core%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Apani%20Dhani%20Ecolodge%20won%20the%20Responsible%20Tourism%20Award%20from%20Wild%20Asia%20in%20the%20category%20Best%20in%20Cultural%20Preservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCqc91JiPkH7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCqc91JiPkH7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_c