k%20its%20location.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Atul%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20himself.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20huge%20decision%20to%20take%20an%20early%20retirement%20but%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20direction%20of%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20his%20wallet%20got%20stolen%20when%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20an%20event.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20at%20this%20event%20that%20I%20met%20my%20co-founder%20who%20was%20herself%20in%20a%20similar%20dilemma%20as%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Purvi%20was%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311375%2Fvishakha-asana-angrakha-size-inclusive-fashion-clothing-brand-fat-tax-shark-tank-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efashion%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20designed%20clothing%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20office%20wear.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20have%20quite%20a%20fight%20to%20become%20a%20designer%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20My%20family%20was%20always%20against%20my%20decision%20and%20wanted%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20traditional%20degree.%20However%2C%20after%20all%20the%20fights%2C%20I%20did%20not%20find%20my%20work%20to%20be%20fulfilling.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20dilemma%20and%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20had%20some%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20duo%20met%20and%20Atul%20expressed%20how%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20around%20travel%20safety%2C%20Purvi%20decided%20to%20jump%20on%20the%20opportunity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20we%20both%20decided%20to%20collaborate%20to%20start%20Arista%20Vault%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Atul%20and%20Purvi%2