a-village-1709127406-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-1709127406-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-1709127406-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20village%E2%80%99s%20plight%20continued%20until%202019%20when%20Meenakshi%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20village%20head.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20Gadge%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20village%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20sarpanch%20madam%20had%20been%20advocating%20for%20social%20work%20from%20the%20time%20when%20she%20was%20not%20even%20elected%20as%20the%20village%20head.%20And%20today%20her%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20community.%20We%20not%20only%20use%20the%20toilets%20in%20our%20homes%20but%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20segregate%20our%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%2C%20who%20also%20works%20with%20the%20mandal%20parishad%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20constituency%20of%20the%20village%2C%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20village%20has%20become%20a%20model%20for%20408%20gram%20panchayats%20in%20the%20state.%20Today%2C%20many%20sarpanches%20from%20other%20districts%20visit%20our%20village%20to%20witness%20how%20we%20achieved%20this%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20village%20has%20utilised%20Rs%2036%20crores%20as%20funds%20from%20the%20state%20and%20the%20central%20government%20to%20successfully%20implement%20various%20government%20programmes%20and%20achieve%20the%20change.%20Other%20than%20the%20official%20help%2C%20Meenakshi%20credits%20the%20community%20for%20the%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20panchayat%20is%20entitled%20to%20the%20same%20fun