20adult%20dogs%20while%20the%20rest%20are%20old%2C%20abandoned%20and%20suffer%20from%20other%20disabilities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20six%20full-time%20staff%20members%20(all%20women)%2C%20Sarah%20and%20Gerry%20spend%20their%20days%20feeding%2C%20treating%2C%20rehabilitating%2C%20and%20caring%20for%20these%20forgotten%20creatures.%20Despite%20their%20abiding%20love%20for%20these%20dogs%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20task.%20From%20offering%20lifelong%20care%20for%20these%20abandoned%20dogs%20to%20raising%20funds%20for%20them%2C%20these%20five%20years%20have%20been%20extremely%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Sarah%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20see%20a%20video%20of%20a%20dog%20suffering%20or%20people%20ask%20you%20to%20rescue%20a%20dog%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20no.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20only%20option%20for%20old%2C%20blind%20or%20paraplegic%20dogs%20is%20euthanasia.%20Nobody%20will%20let%20them%20survive%20on%20the%20street.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20live%20with%20the%20guilt%20of%20refusing%20shelter%20to%20a%20dog%20who%20needs%20it.%20I%20would%20rather%20see%20them%20alive%20than%20put%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dog%20Shelter%20and%20Home%20by%20MARS%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-768x432.jpg%20768